    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable option for anyone prioritizing functionality over aesthetics. The exterior has several visible scratches, some minor door dings, and the clear coat is starting to show its age on the roof. Inside, the upholstery shows noticeable wear and a few small stains, though the cabin remains smoke-free. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need routine maintenance like new brake pads and tires in the near future. It\u2019s an honest car that gets the job done without any surprises.",
