    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. It serves as a reliable and comfortable drive, perfect for someone looking for a quality vehicle without the 'new car' price tag. While the exterior and interior are generally very clean, you may find some minor signs of wear, such as light surface scratches or small interior scuffs, consistent with careful use. Mechanically, the car is sound and ready for the road, offering a smooth driving experience and dependable performance.",
