    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of pre-owned quality, presenting in a condition that rivals a new car sitting on a showroom floor. The exterior is finished in a deep, lustrous paint that has been professionally ceramic-coated, offering a mirror-like reflection completely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Every panel gap is laser-straight, and the factory alloy wheels are immaculate, showing no signs of curb rash or oxidation. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of perfection; the premium leather seats are supple and taut, showing zero bolster wear or creasing, and still carry that distinct new-car aroma. The dashboard and trim pieces are devoid of any scratches or sun-fading, and every electronic component\u2014from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate control\u2014operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, benefiting from a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule performed exclusively at authorized service centers. It has been stored in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen inclement weather. This is a rare, investment-grade find for a buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
